  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Fortuna</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>I'm dying just like everyone else </l>
          <l>resting at ease </l>
          <l>no one comes near </l>
          <l>light years from my bed </l>
          <l>just like everyone says </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>it used to be a part of the deal </l>
          <l>don't be yourself </l>
          <l>always conceal </l>
          <l>don't feel </l>
          <l>just pretend </l>
          <l>just like everyone can </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>you won't get me now </l>
          <l>you won't get me now </l>
          <l>it's harder when my meaning have no words </l>
          <l>might as well give numbers to explain my life </l>
          <l>to everyone who thinks I'm odd </l>
          <l>nothing's gonna matter when the bombs will fall </l>
          <l>upon us all </l>
          <l>and they will fall </l>
          <l>nothing's gonna make me crawl</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
